     list/⍨←force∨0<⊃∘⎕NC¨list   ⍝ List only those that are around
 :EndIf
 :If 9=#.⎕NC'APLTreeUtils'
     A←#.APLTreeUtils
 :ElseIf 9=⎕NC'APLTreeUtils'
